D). Since self-diffusion is not assessed in DLS measurements, a\nmethod to deduce the MSD approximately in DLS is theoretically validated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Nov 2017 20:51:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-13"}
