onentially, which is\nconsistent with the theoretical prediction of the continuous collisional growth\neven when turbulence-generated collisions are invoked. This consistency only\nreflects the mean effect of turbulence on collisional growth.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Nov 2017 00:23:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 11 Mar 2018 23:18:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 11 Jun 2018 07:51:56 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 12 Jun 2018 19:58:29 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Wed, 15 Aug 2018 13:26:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-14"}
