icant as the smallest model exhibiting stratification.\nStratified manifold-sheaf pairs - sheaves adding useful local and global\nstructure to general bundles - lie at the heart of Shape Theory's future\ndevelopment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Nov 2017 04:20:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 14 Feb 2018 23:17:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-16"}
